title: Satchel's Pizza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Eclectic local pizza place offering vegan cheese. Vegans ask for vegan crust and no cheese in house salad. Also has tempeh on pies or calzones. Pesto is vegan. Local artist materials and occasional music. Salvage shop in the back; behind that a music venue where you can eat your pizza. May be a long wait during busy times.
